14:20 Bléssed the mán who wáits upon wísdom,
and pónders her jústice,
and reflécts upon the wáys of Gód.

15:3 She will féed him with the bréad of understánding,
with the wáter of léarning to drínk,

4 He will rést on her and not fáll,
trúst in her and nót be shámed;

5a She will exált him above his compánions,
6b and he will inhérit an everlásting náme.
